* Databricks Runtime
** What it is
***_ Customized Apache Spark builds
***_ Performance improvements
***_ Additional libraries included
** Specialized Versions
***_ General data processing
***_ Machine Learning runtime
***_ Graph processing
***_ Genomics
** Version Management
***_ Multiple versions available
***_ Long-Term Support (LTS) releases
***_ Specifies Spark version & dates
** Lifecycle Stages
***_ Legacy: available, not recommended
***_ Deprecated: marked for removal
***_ End of Support: no more patches
***_ End of Life: retired, unavailable
** Maintenance Updates
***_ Apply by restarting cluster
@endmindmap
